y acquire on the way, and not lose sight of the real objective.\r\nThe fourth and final chapter, Kaivalya Pāda, or Absolute Freedom reached by the yogis whose consciousness is pure and free from the movements of nature. Dharma-meghaḥ samādhi, the fruit of yoga brings the end of afflictions and karma.', 'Yoga Sutras', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-16 16:24:48', '2013-11-16 16:24:48', '', 17, 'http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
