INSERT INTO `wpydnv_posts` VALUES (227, 1, '2013-12-07 12:00:33', '2013-12-07 12:00:33', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-201" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;" title="Yoga Loft Bristol" alt="YogaLoftLogoAddress" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/YogaLoftLogoAddress-e1386005646620.png" width="600" height="152" />\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 28px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">New!</span> Evening Yoga Class at Yoga Loft, Bristol </span>\r\n\r\nI\'m taking over from Juliet, who is moving out of Bristol, the Thursday evening class. I\'ll be teaching it from 27th March 2014!\r\n<h4>Thursday - General</h4>\r\n<em>6 - 7.30pm</em>\r\nThis class has been running for a long time and I\'m looking forward to be teaching it. It\'s a well rounded class suitable for all.\r\n\r\n<strong>Drop-in Rate</strong> - per class: £10\r\n\r\n<strong>Regulars Yogacard</strong> - 10 classes/ 12 weeks: £90 (Also Lunchtime \'Regulars Yogacard\' can be used with £2 supplement)\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 28px;">Lunchtime Yoga Classes at Yoga Loft, Bristol </span>\r\n\r\nI\'m teaching 4 new lunchtime classes at Yogaloft: every Mon, Wed, Thu &amp; Fri 1 - 2pm\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="font-family: Bitter, Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3;">Monday - Beginners </span></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nStep by step introduction to the basic yoga postures. Perfect for yoga novices or those who like to brush up on yoga foundation in this progressively structured class. All standing poses will be practiced regularly and you will learn to do Shoulder Stand and variations here. All other groups of poses will be also introduced.\r\n<h4>Wednesday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a class for all levels from beginners to improvers. We will be focusing on different postures every week and basic breathing techniques will also be taught.\r\n<h4>Thursday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nDynamic class suitable for all. All basic yoga postures will be taught including shoulder stand and relaxation.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Bitter, Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3;"><strong>Friday -</strong> <strong>Restorative</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a slower pace class suitable for all levels. Poses will be practised aimed at helping the body recover at the end of the week. The timing in the poses is prolonged for a deeper experience. More attention is given to the breath and basic breathing exercises will be taught regularly in this class.\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Classes are suitable for all, no previous yoga experience needed!</span>\r\n<h3>Just Drop In!</h3>\r\nAll classes are drop in, but if you have any questions or need to tell us something, please use <a title="Contact" href="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/contact/">this form</a>.\r\n<h1><span style="font-size: 24px;">Prices</span></h1>\r\n<h4>1 hour Lunchtime Class</h4>\r\n<h4><img class="wp-image-360 alignleft" style="border: 1px solid black; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 10px;" alt="Yoga Card" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/YogaCard-small.jpg" width="217" height="138" /></h4>\r\n<strong>Frequent Yogacard</strong> - 10 classes/ 6 weeks: £49\r\n\r\n<strong>Regulars Yogacard</strong> - 10 classes/ 12 weeks: £70\r\n\r\n<img class="alignright  wp-image-172" style="margin: 10px;" title="£49 for 10 classes" alt="£49 for 10 Classes" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/49for10circle-300x300.png" width="144" height="144" /><strong>Drop-in Rate</strong> - per class: £8\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>About The Teacher</h3>\r\nAndrea is an experienced Iyengar Yoga teacher with a friendly and compassionate teaching style. She places great focus on attention to detail and the individual needs of her students. <a title="About Me" href="http://localhost:8888/wpyog